#: src/Admin/Admin.php
msgid "API Key Configuration"
msgstr "API 密钥配置"

#: src/Admin/Admin.php
msgid "Please configure your API Key in the Settings > Connectors page. The API Key is required for the provider to be activated."
msgstr "请在设置 > 连接器页面配置您的 API 密钥。API 密钥是激活提供商所必需的。"

#: src/Admin/Admin.php
msgid "Text Generation is using default values (OpenAI). To use a different provider, enter your custom Base URL and Model Name below, then click Save."
msgstr "文本生成正在使用默认值 (OpenAI)。要使用其他提供商，请在下方输入您的 Base URL 和模型名称，然后点击保存。"

#: src/Admin/Admin.php
msgid "Image Generation is using default values (OpenAI). To use a different provider, enter your custom Base URL and Model Name below, then click Save."
msgstr "图像生成正在使用默认值 (OpenAI)。要使用其他提供商，请在下方输入您的 Base URL 和模型名称，然后点击保存。"

